  "text": "Similar results for 1 < p ≤ 5 seem to be open. Numerical and analytical arguments in [CITATION_1] suggest that the rate of convergence of solutions in case (2) to solitons should depend strongly on the nonlinearity: for p = 3, the expected rate is t −1/2 and slower for 1 < p < 3.",
